resources.string:
For the first time using the software, follow the tips to turn on your Bluetooth. Or, find the Bluetooth option in the "Settings" in your phone, and then turn on Bluetooth to receive data. 
The followings are the necessary steps to do before the measurement: 
1. Click the icon to open the bluetooth scale APP; 
2. Turn on the bluetooth; 
3. Make sure you enter the body parameters (gender, height and age) and your data are correct; 
4. After setting, please stand barefoot on the scale, and then wait for the test is completed to receive data; 
5. Leave the scale surface after data reception.
